snippet.title: Amber Heard, Eva Longoria, Andie MacDowell and more at the L'Oréal Paris 'Women of Worth'
snippet.description:
Amber, Eva, Andie and more L'Oréal spokespeople took part to the L'Oréal Paris 'Women of Worth' celebrations in New York. On the red carpet Amber spoke about gender discriminations and the Time's Up movement and the huge gains it has made over these months.
